<!-- cache hit 72:single/related:413018abf0fc38bba33a4ee41288e7e6 --><!-- empty -->
<p>Good morning, Ars readers! I'll keep this extremely short: Our friends at Wired have been tracking <a href="https://www.wired.com/story/best-prime-day-deals-2024/">the best deals for Amazon Prime Day</a>, and we are syndicating their work here for anyone at Ars who might want to peruse the deals that are still live today. Enjoy!</p>
<h3>Laptop deals</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/3Y5enro">Apple MacBook Air (13 inch, 2024)</a> for $849 with coupon ($250 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/3zLIM3Y">Lenovo IdeaPad 1 laptop, 15.6-inch</a> for $290 ($50 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/464OFFz">Lenovo Special Business Edition laptop, 15.6-inch</a> for $650 with coupon ($150 off)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Keyboard deals</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/4czxtKN">Logitech Pop Keys mechanical wireless keyboard</a> for $66 ($34 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/4f5tPKa">SteelSeries Apex 7 TKL mechanical gaming keyboard</a> for $70 ($21 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/4bO5Cp9">GMMK 2 mechanical gaming keyboard</a> for $80 ($30 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/4bHlfyB">Corsair K100 mechanical gaming keyboard</a> for $175 ($45 off)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Gaming deals</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/3y2LNMS">SCUF Instinct Pro wireless Xbox controller</a> for $195 ($35 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/3y0GI7E">Seagate 1-TB Xbox Series X/S storage expansion card</a> for $123 ($27 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/4cIDsgq">Alienware AW3423DW 34-Inch Ultrawide gaming monitor</a> for $854 ($246 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/3Y64qdx">Plugable 12-in-1 USB-C triple monitor docking station</a> for $160 ($40 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/3Wa7wKC">Arzopa Z1FC portable monitor</a> for $117 ($53 off)</li>
<li><a href="https://amzn.to/3W68844">Meta Quest 3 VR headset</a> for $430 ($70 off)</li>
</ul>
<h3>TV deals</h3>
<ul>
